Using this approach, the affinity (Kd) of the interaction between FcγRIIIa (FF genotype) and wild type, or parental, Fc was determined to be 387 nM while the affinity of variant I332E was 52 nM.
Glycoengineered antibody (GnTIII) displayed a Kd of 83 nM while a combinatorial variant (L256P, I332E) displayed a Kd of 21 nM.
